HashKnownHosts no
VisualHostKey yes
CheckHostIP yes
NoHostAuthenticationForLocalhost yes

## Debian hosts
Host master ravel alioth
     HostName %h.debian.org
Host *.debian.net
     User rak
Host *.debian.org master ravel alioth
     User rak
     StrictHostKeyChecking yes
     UserKnownHostsFile ~/.ssh/known_hosts.d/debian
